rows.label: bf11490150_0010
rows.name: What about this man?

rows.label: bf11490150_0020
rows.name: Picked him up while I was collecting Cores.

rows.label: bf11490150_0025
rows.name: He was one of your pawns, right?

rows.label: bf11490150_0030
rows.name:
I just had him work as a Core broker for you. 
othing more.

rows.label: bf11490150_0040
rows.name: He's basically human garbage.

rows.label: bf11490150_0050
rows.name: Can't argue with that.

rows.label: bf11490150_0060
rows.name: So what are you going to do with him?

rows.label: bf11490150_0070
rows.name: Whether he's scum or trash, he has his uses.

rows.label: bf11490150_0080
rows.name: That plan I mentioned to you...

rows.label: bf11490150_0085
rows.name: I was thinking it's time to get it started.

rows.label: bf11490150_0090
rows.name: Is that... a Blade Eater?

rows.label: bf11490150_0100
rows.name: He'll become stronger. Many times over.

rows.label: bf11490150_0110
rows.name: So much so that a Man-Eater won't even compare.

rows.label: bf11490150_0120
rows.name: Can you control him?

rows.label: bf11490150_0130
rows.name: Nah, don't worry even if I can't.

rows.label: bf11490150_0140
rows.name: He's just the first prototype, after all.

rows.label: bf11490150_0145
rows.name:
He's fated to have his tissues break down
and die sooner or later.

rows.label: bf11490150_0150
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf11490150_0160
rows.name: I hear...

rows.label: bf11490150_0165
rows.name: he has a history with the secret treasure of Iira.

rows.label: bf11490150_0167
rows.name: He'll come in handy one way or another.

rows.label: bf11490150_0170
rows.name: Iira?

rows.label: bf11490150_0175
rows.name: So you are worried about him? About Metsu?

rows.label: bf11490150_0180
rows.name: It's about what comes after.
